Search for a text in a file 
68. grep - used to search for a string in a file. grep "String to check"  pathtofile/filename.extension
69. zgrep - used to search for a sting in a zip file containing documents. zgrep "String to check"  pathtofile/filename.extension
70. cat - used to display a text file in teminal - cat pathtofile/filename.extension
71. less - used to display a text file in teminal along with features like scrolling from top to bottom of text and search for a string. less pathtofile/filename.extension


